🎥 Q12: “Global Must-Watch 🌍🎬”

Points: 💎 20 points

Task:
For every language, crown the ultimate must-watch movie:

🗣️ Language

🎬 Title

📅 Release Year

⭐ Highest Rating

Only 1 movie per language makes the cut → the one with the highest rating (if tied, pick the earliest release).

💡 Hints:

Join Movies + Ratings by movie_id.

Use ROW_NUMBER() to rank movies per language by rating DESC, tie-breaking with release year ASC.

Pick only rn = 1 → the champ movie per language.

Sort results alphabetically by language.

⚡ Difficulty: Polyglot Cinephile 🎞️✨
